# =============================================================================
# Reference material (third-party screenshots, not project assets)
# =============================================================================
# Local-only reference dirs the operator created from his pre-bot Discord
# server. Named with the platform's original "GoldRush" name; left as-is
# because they're untracked operator artefacts (renaming them on disk is
# the operator's call). DeathRoll-named equivalents also ignored for forward-
# compat in case the operator does rename them.
GoldRush Luck/
GoldRush Poker/
DeathRoll Luck/
DeathRoll Poker/
*.dump
*.dump.gpg

